 <arm>
   <uof name="Property_assignment">
      <description>
The Property_assignment UoF specifies the data structure for the assignment of properties to product data.
<note number="1">This module enables to associate a property type to an object and one or more representations of the considered property.
</note>
<note number="2">
The values, geometric models, texts which provide a representation of a property assigned to some object, may specify 
required, computed, estimated, observed or measured characteristics of the considered object, depending, in particular, on whether the object is a virtual one or an tangible object existing in real world.
</note>
      </description>   
      <uof.ae entity="Assigned_property"/>
      <uof.ae entity="Applied_independent_property"/>
      <uof.ae entity="Property_representation"/>
   </uof>
  
